A real-time, network-based Intrusion Detection System (IDS) with a professional SOC-style dashboard, built using Python, Scapy, Flask, Socket.IO, and Machine Learning.

This project monitors live network traffic, detects suspicious behavior, and visualizes alerts and Wi-Fi usage in real time through a modern web dashboard.

